---
import Ps5Icon from "@/assets/ps5.svg"
import XboxIcon from "@/assets/xbox.svg"
---

<!-- Section: Next-Gen Features -->
<section id="features" class="scroll-mt-28 space-y-16 py-12 relative z-10">
  <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-4 reveal-on-scroll">
    <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-pink-500 uppercase bg-pink-500/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-pink-500/20">
      Tecnología de Vanguardia
    </span>
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">EXPERIENCIA DE NUEVA GENERACIÓN</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 font-narrow text-base md:text-lg">
      Grand Theft Auto VI aprovecha al máximo el hardware de última generación para ofrecer el mundo abierto más inmersivo jamás creado.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 reveal-section">
    <!-- Feature 1: Ray Tracing -->
    <div class="reveal-item group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 hover:border-pink-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 size-24 rounded-full bg-pink-500/5 blur-xl group-hover:bg-pink-500/10 transition-colors"></div>
      <div class="size-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-pink-500/15">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M6 3h12l4 6-10 13L2 9z" />
          <path d="M11 3 8 9l4 13 4-13-3-6" />
          <path d="M2 9h20" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Trazado de Rayos</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-narrow leading-relaxed">
        Iluminación global realista, reflejos dinámicos en el agua de las playas y sombras físicas detalladas en tiempo real.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 2: 3D Audio -->
    <div class="reveal-item group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 hover:border-purple-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 size-24 rounded-full bg-purple-500/5 blur-xl group-hover:bg-purple-500/10 transition-colors"></div>
      <div class="size-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/15">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2" />
          <path d="M16.24 7.76a6 6 0 0 1 0 8.49" />
          <path d="M7.76 16.24a6 6 0 0 1 0-8.49" />
          <path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.14" />
          <path d="M4.93 19.07a10 10 0 0 1 0-14.14" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Audio Espacial 3D</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-narrow leading-relaxed">
        Siente el rugido de los motores deportivos y la dirección del bullicio de Vice City con una inmersión acústica tridimensional de alta precisión.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 3: Performance -->
    <div class="reveal-item group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 hover:border-orange-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 size-24 rounded-full bg-orange-500/5 blur-xl group-hover:bg-orange-500/10 transition-colors"></div>
      <div class="size-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-pink-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-orange-500/15">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" />
          <rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6" />
          <line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4" />
          <line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4" />
          <line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23" />
          <line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23" />
          <line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9" />
          <line x1="20" y1="15" x2="23" y2="15" />
          <line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9" />
          <line x1="1" y1="15" x2="4" y2="15" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Rendimiento Fluido</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-narrow leading-relaxed">
        Modos visuales optimizados que equilibran resoluciones nativas en 4K y una tasa constante de 60 fotogramas por segundo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 4: Haptics -->
    <div class="reveal-item group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 hover:border-pink-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 size-24 rounded-full bg-pink-500/5 blur-xl group-hover:bg-pink-500/10 transition-colors"></div>
      <div class="size-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-pink-500/15">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M12 10a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v3a2 2 0 0 0 4 0v-3a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z" />
          <path d="M14 10a4 4 0 0 0-8 0v4a1 1 0 0 0 2 0v-4a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v5a1 1 0 0 0 2 0v-5z" />
          <path d="M8 14v2a1 1 0 0 0 2 0v-2a1 1 0 0 0-2 0z" />
          <path d="M16 14v1a1 1 0 0 0 2 0v-1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0z" />
          <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-10 10v3a1 1 0 0 0 2 0v-3a8 8 0 0 1 16 0v3a1 1 0 0 0 2 0v-3A10 10 0 0 0 12 2z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Gatillos Hápticos</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-narrow leading-relaxed">
        Siente la tracción del terreno, los disparos y la vibración de las colisiones mediante la respuesta háptica avanzada de los mandos modernos.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
